his job. GARY AMBROSE / Los Angeles Times; Table, PLANNED TRANSPORTATION 
CORRIDORS, Los Angeles Times ; Map, PLANNED TRANSPORTATION CORRIDORS, Los 
Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
