<HEADLINE>
<P>
WASHINGTON'S BIRTHDAY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Today is Washington's Birthday. The following will be closed in observance of 
the holiday: 
</P>
<P>
* All county, state, and federal offices. 
</P>
<P>
* All public elementary, junior and high schools, and all colleges and 
universities, including community colleges. 
</P>
<P>
* County, state and federal courthouses. 
</P>
<P>
* County libraries. 
</P>
<P>
* All city offices, with the exception of Westminster. 
</P>
<P>
* All banks and savings and loans. 
</P>
<P>
Mail: All post offices will be closed and there will be no mail delivery. Mail 
will be collected from mailboxes according to the posted holiday schedule. 
</P>
<P>
Trash: There will be regular trash pickup by city and county refuse workers. 
</P>
<P>
Buses: Orange County Transit District buses will run on regular schedule. There 
will be dial-a-ride and car-pool services available on the holiday. 
</P>
<P>
Parks: All city- and county-run parks and recreation facilities will be open 
during regular hours. 
</P>
</TEXT>
