Game Story 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA021990-0103 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 178892 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
February 19, 1990, Monday, Orange County Edition 
